  "detailed_description": "<h1>Special Offer</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857580/extras/ff5149d1d8e09021af31fa3907c251ed.avif?t=1662667634\" width=610 height=130 /></span><br><br>The main goal of this game is to get achievements. You don't even need to play it – the game itself will give them to you. If you're polite to her…<br><br>This is a short sketch exploring such a phenomenon in the world of computer games as \"trophy hunting\". Complete the tasks that the game gives you, get all-new achievements for them, test yourself – will you dare to collect them all?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857580/extras/69565ce0e0ae3c4269e6b3ee9d7a448b.poster.avif?t=1662667634\" width=610 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857580/extras/69565ce0e0ae3c4269e6b3ee9d7a448b.webm?t=1662667634\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857580/extras/69565ce0e0ae3c4269e6b3ee9d7a448b.mp4?t=1662667634\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Is this a visual novel?<br>Is this a dating simulator?<br>Is this an experiment?<br>This:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Short duration<br></li><li>Psychedelic pixel visual style<br></li><li>Many achievements<br></li><li>A lot of achievements!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857580/extras/06619eedb0498f0cf3741a00728a2c7f.poster.avif?t=1662667634\" width=610 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857580/extras/06619eedb0498f0cf3741a00728a2c7f.webm?t=1662667634\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857580/extras/ff5149d1d8e09021af31fa3907c251ed.avif?t=1662667634\" width=610 height=130 /></span><br><br>The main goal of this game is to get achievements. You don't even need to play it – the game itself will give them to you. If you're polite to her…<br><br>This is a short sketch exploring such a phenomenon in the world of computer games as \"trophy hunting\". Complete the tasks that the game gives you, get all-new achievements for them, test yourself – will you dare to collect them all?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857580/extras/69565ce0e0ae3c4269e6b3ee9d7a448b.poster.avif?t=1662667634\" width=610 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857580/extras/69565ce0e0ae3c4269e6b3ee9d7a448b.webm?t=1662667634\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857580/extras/69565ce0e0ae3c4269e6b3ee9d7a448b.mp4?t=1662667634\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Is this a visual novel?<br>Is this a dating simulator?<br>Is this an experiment?<br>This:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Short duration<br></li><li>Psychedelic pixel visual style<br></li><li>Many achievements<br></li><li>A lot of achievements!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857580/extras/06619eedb0498f0cf3741a00728a2c7f.poster.avif?t=1662667634\" width=610 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857580/extras/06619eedb0498f0cf3741a00728a2c7f.webm?t=1662667634\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
